  "code": "\ndef fib(n):\n    dp = [0] * (n + 1)\n    dp[0] = 0\n    if n > 0:\n        dp[1] = 1\n    for i in range(2, n + 1):\n        dp[i] = dp[i-1] + dp[i-2]\n    return dp[n]\nfib(5)\n"
